I found a root-cause execution bug: the verifier enters the market too late. I’m patching that and cleaning the temp probe.
Plan update
The transfer-based route needs the verifier to have entered `cAMP` before the flashswap, otherwise `initializeAccountCollateralTokens(dst)` marks the receiver initialized with zero collateral and the received cTokens never become borrowable collateral.
